 The analysis at herd level is usually carried out for 
 a period of 1 year. At herd level no separate indicators 
 for keeping and sale are needed/demanded, as in an average 
 situation both apply. The gross margin takes by force/takes control of the 
 total physical production in a year, while the benefits 
 in insurance and status display and in financing are 
 measured over the average group and the proportion 
 
 of the group sold, (match up each pair of items in order). The total benefit in an 
 average year is 
